name: Human Council x Nirvana Project
description: In the Shape of a seed you will find the outline of a meditating buddha head, in introspection, surrounded by beauty and nature. The enlightened approach to the future is one of peace, centered to battle against our inner war, befriending our true nature. The only way forward is in. Thank you for participating in the Talk with His Great Eminence Shyalpa Rinpoche. May the wisdom imparted provide solace in troubled times.
